further nuclear explosion by the Indian government, The Indian
Express said Saturday.
</P>
<P>
in a recent nine-page letter to the Chief Justice of India, the
Scientific Workers' Forum and other organizations also urged the
Chief Justice to stay all official propaganda of the government of
India in support of the test, nuclear explosions.
</P>
<P>
