outstanding season, while Giuseppe Bergomi, veteran of Italy's
World Cup triumph in Spain '82, was called back to be part of the
second string with the full backing of the other defenders.
</P>
<P>
Del Piero will arrive at the national training camp at
Coverciano this evening for tests. A press conference will be
held after although no definitive decision is expected on his
chances for going to France next month. 
