<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, May 22 (Xinhua) -- Italian Prime Minister Romano Prodi
said Friday that his government is strongly in favor of a
continued presence of the multi-national peace-keeping force in
Macedonia to safeguard its territorial integrity.
</P>
<P>
