Crvenkoski, Prodi expressed Italy's support for the "Multimodal
Corridor Number 8," which would help establish an integrated
communication link between the southern Italian port city of Bari
and the Bulgarian city of Varna on the Black Sea, via the Albanian
port city of Durres and the Macedonian capital of Skopje.
</P>
<P>
