Macedonia played in the Balkans, particularly in the recent
developments in Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
He added that he would like to see relations between Macedonia
and the European Union bolstered.
</P>
<P>
Crvenkoski, in return, stressed his country's keen interest in
the rapid stipulation of an association agreement with the EU.
