Special Forces (Kopassus) Maj. Gen. Muchdi Purwopranjono would be
replaced by Maj. Gen. Syahrir M.S. who is currently chief of the
Udayano Military Command which oversees Bali, West and East Nusa
Tenggara and East Timor. 
