<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Venezuelan Crudes Basket to Close This Year at 13 Dollars </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CARACAS, May 22 (Xinhua) -- The average price of the Venezuelan
crudes basket will close this year at 13 U.S. dollars per barrel,
local specialists said.
</P>
<P>
Although the international crudes prices started to show a
dipping trend, such movement will not be reflected immediately on
the Venezuelan basket value, explained the specialists.
</P>
<P>
"The Venezuelan crudes basket is a combination of crudes and
byproducts and it is impossible to know its day to day price. The
prices drop undergone in the recent days will affect us, but there
still is an expectation to close the year at a 13 dollar per
barrel average," said Cesar Baena, an oil specialist.
</P>
<P>
Erwin Arrieta, Venezuelan energy and mines minister, said that
the average price of the Venezuelan crudes basket was 11 dollars
by the middle of the week. 
</P>
</TEXT>
