<HEADLINE> U.S. Electronics Sales up 10.6 Percent in First Quarter </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW YORK, May 22 (Xinhua) -- U.S. factory sales of electronics
equipment totaled almost 119 billion U.S. dollars in the first
quarter, up 10.6 percent from the same period 1997, the Electronic
Industries Alliance reported on Friday.
</P>
<P>
